roups are a liability. More lag, more mana spent on a clericless tank, and so forth. <br><br>Another thing to consider is that he has 32K hit points. Just do that damage, and do it fast.<br><br><br><br>Good luck,<br>Trulian Swiftblade<br> <p><IMG SRC="http://www.geocities.com/janus_of_ul/ringostarr.bmp"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uaakla2.showPublicProfile?language=EN>aakla2</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_thatch.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 36<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/23/02 12:29:41 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=483.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   re</span><hr size=1> when doing a vox raid and you rush the lair, if you see the first 1 or 2 poeple fall through the floor STOP your going the wrong way. very nasty bear pit below you. <br><br>get as much   FR or CR as you can and try to get in a group with a bard. when you attack dont kick taunt or disarm(whatever your 4th hot key is) your lvl 45 if you get agro your dead and wont help anyone. not doing these will lower your chances of getting agro. also switch your weapons for ones that dont proc anything. procing weapons can cause nasty agro sometimes.<br><br><br>the only thing you want from Vox/Nagy are RBB or CoF or a bag if you want. there is also a res staff but depending on your server and who holds the raid it might be forfieted to the guild when it drops. dont go in for anything else because it will be obsolete in a few levels. only the bag rbb and cof will be with you for a long time. dont go in for gay loot just to sell it when others there will use it, that is frowned upon.<br><br><br><br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcol